	</ol>
	<div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
		<div class="item active">
			<img src="~/images/banner2.png" alt="ASP.NET" class="img-responsive" />
			<div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
				<p>
					Archysoft is a young creative team with great business experience of each employee
					<a class="btn btn-default" href="https://www.upwork.com/agencies/~0193b59699409cccdd">
						Learn More
					</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="item">
			<img src="~/images/banner1.png" alt="Visual Studio" class="img-responsive" />
			<div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
				<p class="blue-caption">
					Archysoft specialty is a huge .NET projects with a lot of complex logics
					<a class="btn btn-info" href="https://www.upwork.com/agencies/~0193b59699409cccdd">
						Learn More
